info.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued December 24 at 3:46AM CST until December 24 at 7:00AM CST by NWS Duluth
info.description: ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 AM CST THIS MORNING IN THE ARROWHEAD... * WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog in the Arrowhead. * WHERE...Northern Cook and Lake, Southern Cook, and Southern Lake Counties. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Grand Portage Reservation.This also includes the Boundary Waters eastern and central area. * WHEN...Until 7 AM CST this morning. * IMPACTS...Low visibility could make driving conditions hazardous.
info.instruction: If driving, slow down, use your low-beam headlights and fog lights, and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.
